    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An exceptional example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This chassis is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe, fresh rod bearings, and a complete cooling system overhaul. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, and the variable M differential lock ensures peak cornering performance. Clad in pristine paint with no oxidation, the interior features original Nappa leather with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
