    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that remains in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and reflects the highest standards of automotive care. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, glass-like finish free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. All body panels are perfectly aligned with factory-spec gaps, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, without a single hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no bolster wear, creasing, or UV fading. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. It drives with the same tightness and precision as the day it was delivered. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic, complete with all original keys, manuals, and a thick binder of maintenance records.",
      "price": 48950.0,
