      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered every single day. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014spotless inside and out! If you've been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
