    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six powerplant. This example exhibits a flawless mechanical pedigree, with a comprehensive service history detailing recent preventative rod bearing replacement and a full double-VANOS overhaul. The high-revving 3.2L engine breathes through six individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound, having undergone professional subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. The suspension remains tight with factory-spec bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and communicative feedback synonymous with the chassis. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero bolster wear on the interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
